# {{ project_name }} Staging

This stack uses the example `stacks/staging-docker` template.

Run through Angee:

```sh
angee up
angee status
angee logs django --follow
```

The operator can combine file, Django API, and direct Django DB state sources:

```sh
angee operator --file .angee/angee.yaml --state-source file --state-source django-api --django-url {{ django_url }}
angee operator --state-source django-api --state-source django-db --django-url {{ django_url }} --database-url "$DATABASE_URL"
```

Direct Docker Compose is useful for debugging only:

```sh
docker compose -f docker-compose.yaml up --build
```
